high_descs: Walk across the room then turn right to face the sink.
Open the cupboard on the left side below the sink and pick up the purple rag.
Turn to the right and take one step, then turn to the left and face the sink.
Put the purple rag in the sink and turn on the water for three seconds, then turn the water off and pick up the rag.
Turn to the left and take one step then turn to the right.
Put the rag on the right side of the sink.
Turn right and look down to face the cabinet under the sink.
Pick up the dirty rag in the cabinet under the sink.
Look up to face the sink at the left end of the counter.
Wash the rag in the sink and then remove it.
Step to the right to face the counter between the sinks.
Place the clean rag on the counter between the sinks.
anns.task_desc: To clean a rag and place it on the counter between the two sinks.

high_descs: Head to the sink on the right
Open the cabinet, take the purple rag out of the cabinet, close the cabinet
Put the rag in the sink, turn on the water for 3 seconds
Take the rag out of the sink
Put the rag on the counter
anns.task_desc: Take the rag from the cabinet, wash it for 3 seconds
